Class PwdCommandHandler

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandHandler, InvocationHistory, ReplyTextBundleAware

    public class PwdCommandHandler
extends AbstractStubCommandHandler
implements CommandHandler
    CommandHandler for the PWD (Print Working Directory) and XPWD commands. By default, return an empty directory name, along with a reply code of 257. You can customize the returned directory name by setting the directory property.

    Each invocation record stored by this CommandHandler contains no data elements.
